        <b>What is NextToSolve?</b><br />

        NextToSovle is a platform where problems of <a href="http://codeforces.com/">Codeforces</a> are presented
        according to difficulty. The problems are divided in different tags (36 in total). <br />
        Given your CodeForces handle, you can use this site to solve CodeForces problems you have not solved,
        matching your programming skill level.<br /><br />
    </p>
