        <b>How to use it?</b><br />
        From the practice tab you can browse all the problems. Enter your CodeForces handle to get problems suited
        your skill. After solving a problem, refresh to update the page.<br />
        From the compare tab you can compare any number of CodeForces users!<br/><br />

    </p>
